">理系総合職</h2>\n                            </div>\n                            <div>\n                                <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/pic_science_01.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"u-mw100p\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"c-grid _col2_ _narrow01_ _sm-col1_ m-block\">\n                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                <div class=\"m-box _wide_ _boxshadow02_ _hg-100_ u-al-c\">\n                                    <h3 class=\"c-recruit-ttl08\">製造技術</h3>\n                                    <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/ico_science_02.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"u-mb-xs u-sm-mw20p\">\n                                    <p class=\"u-al-l\">生産工程、製造現場や設備の改善、品質管理を行いつつ、自分の技術も磨く、会社の顔となる製品作り、モノづくりを牽引します。部署内外でコミュニケーションを取りながら全員が働きやすい安全な工場づくりを実現します。</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                <div class=\"m-box _wide_ _boxshadow02_ _hg-100_ u-al-c\">\n                                    <h3 class=\"c-recruit-ttl08\">研究開発</h3>\n                                    <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/ico_science_04.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"u-mb-xs u-sm-mw20p\">\n                                    <p class=\"u-al-l\">10年先を見据え、次世代の東北特殊鋼の成長を支える新技術を創出します。積み重ねた独自の技術、産学連携による開発を推進し、当社が提供する技術的価値を高めます。</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"c-recruit-ttl04\">社員インタビュー</h3>\n                            <div class=\"c-grid _col2_ _narrow01_ _sm-col1_ m-block\">\n                                <div class=\"__col\">\n                                    <a href=\"/recruit/occupation/interview/interview01.html\" class=\"m-box _rec-blue_ _hg-100_ _block_ e-text-link _fz-xxl_ _btn_ _navy_ c-recruit-occupation__interview\">\n                                        <div class=\"c-grid _col2_ _narrow02_ _sm-col1_\">\n                                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                                <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/interview/pic_interview_01_thum.png\" alt=\"理系総合職インタビュー\" class=\"\">\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div>\n                                                <p class=\"e-text-mb __link\">\n                                                    <span class=\"__txt\">仕事の質を高め、社内から頼られる存在になりたいですです</span>\n                                                    <span class=\"link-icon\"><span class=\"icon-arrow-right\"></span></span>\n                                                </p>\n                                                <p class=\"e-note u-c-rec-blue\">溶鍛鋼材事業部 鋼材工場<br>鋼材製造チーム　T.O</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </section>\n                    \n                    <section class=\"m-block _mb-xl_ _page-break_\" id=\"liberal-arts\">\n                        <div class=\"c-flex _left_ _sm-fd-c_ m-block\">\n                            <div class=\"c-flex__item u-w25p u-sm-w100p c-recruit-occupation__category\">\n                                <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/ico_liberal-arts_01.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"__ico\">\n                                <h2 class=\"c-recruit-ttl02 u-mb-0\">文系総合職</h2>\n                            </div>\n                            <div>\n                                <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/pic_liberal-arts_01.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"u-mw100p\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"c-grid _col3_ _narrow03_ _sm-col1_ m-block\">\n                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                <div class=\"m-box _wide_ _boxshadow02_ _hg-100_ u-al-c\">\n                                    <h3 class=\"c-recruit-ttl08\">生産管理</h3>\n                                    <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/ico_liberal-arts_02.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"u-mb-xs u-sm-mw20p\">\n                                    <p class=\"u-al-l\">生産管理の役割は、全てが計画どおりに進んでいるかといった大きなところから、日々変わる状況を分析し、適切に判断するといった細かいところにまで及びます。生産にかかわるありとあらゆる事を管理していることから、大切な製品をお客様に確実に届けるための司令塔とも言えます。</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                <div class=\"m-box _wide_ _boxshadow02_ _hg-100_ u-al-c\">\n                                    <h3 class=\"c-recruit-ttl08\">総務・人事・経理</h3>\n                                    <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/ico_liberal-arts_03.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"u-mb-xs u-sm-mw20p\">\n                                    <p class=\"u-al-l\">営業等のフロントオフィスに対して、総務人事、経理等はバックオフィスと呼ばれますが、その活躍フィールドは裏方に留まりません。時には経営そのものに直結するダイナミズムのある施策を通じ、売上、収益に直結する重要な役割を担っています。</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                <div class=\"m-box _wide_ _boxshadow02_ _hg-100_ u-al-c\">\n                                    <h3 class=\"c-recruit-ttl08\">営業職</h3>\n                                    <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/ico_liberal-arts_04.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"u-mb-xs u-sm-mw20p\">\n                                    <p class=\"u-al-l\">緻密な市場、顧客リサーチを行い、それを基にした営業戦略を立てて実行にうつしていくことが営業職の役割です。単に売上を追うのではなく、市場、顧客の要望に応えるために何をすべきか考え、実行し、当社の技術的価値を広めていくことで、企業価値を向上させる重要な役割です。</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"c-recruit-ttl04\">社員インタビュー</h3>\n                            <div class=\"c-grid _col2_ _narrow01_ _sm-col1_ m-block\">\n                                <div class=\"__col\">\n                                    <a href=\"/recruit/occupation/interview/interview02.html\" class=\"m-box _rec-blue_ _hg-100_ _block_ e-text-link _fz-xxl_ _btn_ _navy_ c-recruit-occupation__interview\">\n                                        <div class=\"c-grid _col2_ _narrow02_ _sm-col1_\">\n                                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                                <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/interview/pic_interview_02_thum.png\" alt=\"文系総合職インタビュー\" class=\"\">\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div>\n                                                <p class=\"e-text-mb __link\">\n                                                    <span class=\"__txt\">いろいろな部署とつながりをもてるのが仕事の魅力</span>\n                                                    <span class=\"link-icon\"><span class=\"icon-arrow-right\"></span></span>\n                                                </p>\n                                                <p class=\"e-note u-c-rec-blue\">総務人事部 総務チーム　Y.O</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </section>\n                    \n                    <section class=\"m-block _mb-xl_ _page-break_\" id=\"ability\">\n                        <div class=\"c-flex _left_ _sm-fd-c_ m-block\">\n                            <div class=\"c-flex__item u-w25p u-sm-w100p c-recruit-occupation__category\">\n                                <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/ico_ability_01.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"__ico\">\n                                <h2 class=\"c-recruit-ttl02 u-mb-0\">技能職</h2>\n                            </div>\n                            <div>\n                                <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/pic_ability_01.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"u-mw100p\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"c-grid _col2_ _narrow01_ _sm-col1_ m-block\">\n                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                <div class=\"m-box _wide_ _boxshadow02_ _hg-100_ u-al-c\">\n                                    <h3 class=\"c-recruit-ttl08\">製造オペレーター</h3>\n                                    <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/ico_ability_02.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"u-mb-xs u-sm-mw20p\">\n                                    <p class=\"u-al-l\">単に製造設備を操作するだけでなく、より良い製品をより効率よく生産する為に設備改良を行います。また数多くの種類の金属を加工することや、トラブルがあった設備の保全も行っています。</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                <div class=\"m-box _wide_ _boxshadow02_ _hg-100_ u-al-c\">\n                                    <h3 class=\"c-recruit-ttl08\">検査・分析</h3>\n                                    <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/ico_ability_03.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"u-mb-xs u-sm-mw20p\">\n                                    <p class=\"u-al-l\">製造現場における検査、分析は、製品の品質が基準を満たしているかどうかを確認する為に行われるものですが、それだけが役割ではありません。判明した不備や改善点を対象となる製造現場に共有することで、不具合の原因究明、さらなる品質改善の原点となるのが検査、分析の職務です。</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"c-recruit-ttl04\">社員インタビュー</h3>\n                            <div class=\"c-grid _col2_ _narrow01_ _sm-col1_ m-block\">\n                                <div class=\"__col\">\n                                    <a href=\"/recruit/occupation/interview/interview03.html\" class=\"m-box _rec-blue_ _hg-100_ _block_ e-text-link _fz-xxl_ _btn_ _navy_ c-recruit-occupation__interview\">\n                                        <div class=\"c-grid _col2_ _narrow02_ _sm-col1_\">\n                                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                                <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/interview/pic_interview_03_thum.png\" alt=\"技能職インタビュー1\" class=\"\">\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div>\n                                                <p class=\"e-text-mb __link\">\n                                                    <span class=\"__txt\">品質向上に向けて知識や技術を磨いていきたいです。</span>\n                                                    <span class=\"link-icon\"><span class=\"icon-arrow-right\"></span></span>\n                                                </p>\n                                                <p class=\"e-note u-c-rec-blue\">熱処理工場　T.W</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"__col\">\n                                    <a href=\"/recruit/occupation/interview/interview04.html\" class=\"m-box _rec-blue_ _hg-100_ _block_ e-text-link _fz-xxl_ _btn_ _navy_ c-recruit-occupation__interview\">\n                                        <div class=\"c-grid _col2_ _narrow02_ _sm-col1_\">\n                                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                                <img src=\"/common/img/recruit/occupation/interview/pic_interview_04_thum.png\" alt=\"技能職インタビュー2\" class=\"\">\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div>\n                                                <p class=\"e-text-mb __link\">\n                                                    <span class=\"__txt\">新しいことへのチャレンジがモチベーションにつながる</span>\n                                                    <span class=\"link-icon\"><span class=\"icon-arrow-right\"></span></span>\n                                                </p>\n                                                <p class=\"e-note u-c-rec-blue\">精密加工工場　W.S</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </section>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n                \n                <!--============================================== recruit-fnav -->\n                                <div class=\"c-recruit-fnav\">\n                    <div class=\"c-recruit-fnav__inner\">\n                        <div class=\"c-grid _col3_ _narrow01_ _sm-col1_\">\n                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                <a href=\"/recruit/\" class=\"m-box _boxshadow02_ e-text-link _btn_ _navy_ c-recruit-fnav__link\">\n                                    <span class=\"__txt\">採用情報トップページ</span>\n                                    <span class=\"link-icon\"><span class=\"icon-arrow-right\"></span></span>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                <a href=\"/recruit/personality/\" class=\"m-box _boxshadow02_ e-text-link _btn_ _navy_ c-recruit-fnav__link\">\n                                    <span class=\"__txt\">求める人物像</span>\n                                    <span class=\"link-icon\"><span class=\"icon-arrow-right\"></span></span>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"__col\">\n                                 <a href=\"/recruit/occupation/\" class=\"m-box _boxshad